brogue: Brogue is a Roguelike game by Brian Walker.
brogue:
brogue: Move around the dungeon with the mouse, the vi-keys (hjklyubn) or
brogue: keypad keys. The arrow keys will also work, but they do not allow
brogue: diagonal movement. Other commands are as listed in the help screen,
brogue: which you can access by typing a question mark or clicking on the
brogue: "Menu" button at the bottom of the screen.
brogue:
brogue: Your goal is to travel to the 26th subterranean floor of the dungeon,
brogue: retrieve the Amulet of Yendor and return with it to the surface.
